OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of the
OL,4,Cold Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FSTV is proposing to change its news
OL,7,Fservice.
OL,9,FThere will, subject to Ofcom approval,
OL,10,Fbe one news service presented from
OL,11,FGlasgow for both central and northern
OL,12,FScotland.
OL,14,FThe financial situation facing STV is
OL,15,Fserious. It lost 200,000 in the first
OL,16,Fhalf of the year. Advertising is down
OL,17,F5m.
OL,19,FBut there is profound concern amongst
OL,20,Fpoliticians in the north of Scotland.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
