OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of the
OL,4,Cold Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FOf course the question now is whether
OL,7,FOfcom will allow this change.
OL,9,FOr might sone compromise emerge? Or
OL,10,Feven outright rejection?
OL,12,FOfcom is not the poodle some accuse it
OL,13,Fof being.
OL,15,FIn 2013 it helped reinstate a fuller
OL,16,Fnews service for the ITV Border region.
OL,18,FBut since then the marketplace has
OL,19,Fchanged.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
