OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of the
OL,4,Cold Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FAdvertising is down. Linear TV is not
OL,7,Fdead but some clearly prefer on demand.
OL,8,FYounger people are not consuming old
OL,9,Fmedia.
OL,11,FIt is all a very hard circle to square.
OL,13,FMeantime caught in the middle are 30
OL,14,FSTV journalists set to lose their jobs.
OL,16,FIf the change happens, "Grampian" will
OL,17,Fbe the first of the official C3
OL,18,Ffranchise areas of old to completely
OL,19,Fdisappear.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
