OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV losses could see the end of the
OL,4,Cold Grampian region
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt will be fascinating to see if this
OL,7,Fproposal actually goes ahead.
OL,9,FOr will Ofcom and political pressure
OL,10,Flead to the plan being scrapped?
OL,12,FThe plan may make those of us who care
OL,13,Fabout TV's history feel nostalgic for
OL,14,FGrampian.
OL,16,FBut nostalgia and sentiment is not an
OL,17,Fargument for stopping the change.
